⏱️ Stopwatch App

A simple and functional || stopwatch || application built using HTML | CSS | JavaScript. This app allows users to start | pause | reset | track time | with precision — ideal for basic timekeeping tasks.

🔗 Live Demo: [Try the Stopwatch](https://farhanbaber.github.io/stop-watch/)

---

📋 Features

- ▶️ Start the timer
- ⏸️ Pause the timer
- 🔁 Reset to 00:00
- 🕒 Millisecond precision (optional)
- 🖥️ Responsive layout (works on desktop and mobile)

---

 🛠️ Technologies Used

- HTML5 – Page structure  
- CSS3 – Styling and layout  
- JavaScript (ES6) – Timer logic and DOM control    

